96
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,119
won't do her any good.

97
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:31,679
It's better for her to leave.

98
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:32,640
Your Majesty,

99
00:04:32,839 --> 00:04:34,119
