100
00:04:34,119 --> 00:04:34,920
A living Buddha.

101
00:04:35,359 --> 00:04:36,679
Why do you have to

102
00:04:36,679 --> 00:04:38,239
come across someone like Scorpion Liu?

103
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:40,040
