114
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:58,839
Why are you here?

115
00:04:59,079 --> 00:05:00,000
Duan Yunzhang.

116
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,959
I can't believe you and Liu Xie
are bullying a mere woman.

117
00:05:01,959 --> 00:05:02,880
