00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:45,359
Well,

248
00:09:45,359 --> 00:09:47,520
I think "Black Bear" suits her better.

249
00:09:47,719 --> 00:09:49,559
She is not worthy to be a queen after all.

250
00:09:50,239 --> 00:09:51,239
Not only she's unreasonable,

251
00:09:51,239 --> 00:09:52,400
but she has also caused trouble.

252
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,599
All these years, I tried so hard

253
00:09:54,599 --> 00:09:56,239
to make sure that the Emperor
and the Grand Chancellor are on good terms.

254
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,919
But she ruined it just like that.

255
00:09:58,159 --> 00:09:59,640
This is infuriating.

256
00:10:00,159 --> 00:10:02,400
She needs to be punished.

257
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:03,799
Your Majesty.

258
00:10:03,799 --> 00:10:04,760
You must not do that.

259
00:10:05,239 --> 00:10:06,239
Why not?

260
00:10:07,479 --> 00:10:09,000
Punishing the Queen

261
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,559
will only worsen the situation.

262
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:12,440
We would have to explain ourselves
to the Grand Chancellor.

263
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:16,159
What do you suggest, then?

264
00:10:16,359 --> 00:10:17,400
In my opinion,

265
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:18,400
we should

266
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:20,280
leave this matter to His Majesty.

267
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:21,719
His Majesty is wise.

268
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:23,080
He will handle it appropriately.

269
00:10:26,479 --> 00:10:27,239
Fine.

270
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:30,080
This is between them.

271
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:32,640
I'll leave it to Zhang, then.

272
00:10:33,799 --> 00:10:34,400
Yes.

273
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:39,599
Your Majesty.

274
00:10:39,599 --> 00:10:40,479
Slowly.

275
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:42,400
I must teach her a lesson today.

276
00:10:49,159 --> 00:10:49,760
Stop right there.

277
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:52,359
I'm telling you to stop.

278
00:10:53,159 --> 00:10:53,840
Stop.

279
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,359
What? Let go of me.

280
00:10:55,359 --> 00:10:56,400
Don't get physical.

281
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:57,880
How dare you?

282
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,200
You humiliated me in public.

283
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,400
Your insults

284
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:01,919
have defamed the imperial family.

285
00:11:02,039 --> 00:11:02,960
Do you know you are in a serious offense?

286
00:11:03,239 --> 00:11:04,559
The Emperor has gotten mad.

287
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:05,760
I'm terrified.

288
00:11:06,119 --> 00:11:07,280
Go and behead me.

289
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,559
The past emperors were wise with their words.

290
00:11:09,559 --> 00:11:10,039
What about you?

291
00:11:10,039 --> 00:11:11,119
Nothing good comes out of your mouth.

292
00:11:11,119 --> 00:11:12,359
-Believe it or not, I can...
-Yes.

293
00:11:12,359 --> 00:11:13,599
You can kick me out of the palace now.

294
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,520
You are so afraid of Liu Xie.

295
00:11:15,599 --> 00:11:17,200
You're too scared to hit me or kill me.

296
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,799
So chasing me out is the only way
you could think of.

297
00:11:18,799 --> 00:11:20,119
I'll say it again.

298
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:21,760
I'm not scared of Liu Xie.

299
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:23,239
So, you don't want to see me.

300
00:11:23,239 --> 00:11:24,559
Don't worry.

301
00:11:24,559 --> 00:11:26,559
I've said it clearly in the broadcast.

302
00:11:26,719 --> 00:11:27,679
We'll live our own lives.

303
00:11:27,679 --> 00:11:28,880
We will not get in each other's way.

304
00:11:30,719 --> 00:11:33,119
So, please let go of me now.

305
00:11:34,799 --> 00:11:35,080
Stop.

306
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:35,840
What?

307
00:11:38,559 --> 00:11:40,679
It seems like you really don't want to leave.

308
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:41,880
What?

309
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:42,799
Are you deaf?

310
00:11:42,799 --> 00:11:44,159
I said we'll go our separate ways.

311
00:11:44,359 --> 00:11:45,400
That won't do.

312
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:47,080
You're a living person.

313
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,719
I can't just pretend that you don't exist.

314
00:11:49,479 --> 00:11:50,119
(No.)

315
00:11:50,359 --> 00:11:51,359
(I can't leave the palace.)

316
00:11:51,359 --> 00:11:52,719
(Or I won't get to see my mother.)

317
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:55,559
Actually, after giving it some thought,

318
00:11:56,559 --> 00:11:58,840
I think you can stay in the palace.

319
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:01,039
What do you mean?

320
00:12:02,760 --> 00:12:04,559
You and I are married.

321
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,599
Then, we should act as husband and wife.

322
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:09,599
You can't call me names

323
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:11,080
while living in the palace

324
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,239
and eating the food
prepared by the Imperial Kitchen.

325
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,840
I actually don't mind.

326
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,239
But are you sure you can live with that?

327
00:12:15,559 --> 00:12:16,760
What are you trying to say?

328
00:12:16,760 --> 00:12:17,479
It's simple.

329
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:20,080
Laundry, clothes folding, and some chores.

330
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:20,799
You should know how to do them.

331
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:21,520
That's all?

332
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,000
That's easy.

333
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,159
Just wait and see.

334
00:12:25,679 --> 00:12:26,719
I'll be waiting.

335
00:12:29,039 --> 00:12:31,320
(I'll get rid of you this time.)

336
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,520
Young Lady, have some tea.

337
00:12:37,159 --> 00:12:37,840
Thank you.

338
00:12:38,159 --> 00:12:38,960
May I know

339
00:12:39,119 --> 00:12:40,599
when is the Queen returning?

340
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:41,840
I'm afraid I don't know.

341
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:50,119
Young Lady, do not fret.

342
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:51,320
From what I see,

343
00:12:51,520 --> 00:12:53,679
Her Majesty was probably
just bickering with His Majesty.

344
00:12:53,679 --> 00:12:55,599
She doesn't mean what she said.

345
00:12:56,119 --> 00:12:58,320
But Father insisted that I stay in the palace,

346
00:12:58,320 --> 00:13:00,799
saying that there's a misunderstanding
between them.

347
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:02,200
It must be something serious.

348
00:13:02,919 --> 00:13:04,400
In that case,

349
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:06,559
there must be a good reason why she is mad.

350
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:10,400
There are words that you can't say
no matter how mad you are.

351
00:13:10,799 --> 00:13:12,239
I thought

352
00:13:12,239 --> 00:13:13,799
she was kind

353
00:13:14,119 --> 00:13:15,599
even though she was clueless.

354
00:13:15,880 --> 00:13:16,919
But judging from this,

355
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:19,039
she's being unruly

356
00:13:19,039 --> 00:13:20,159
and conceited.

357
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:22,960
Baiyu.

358
00:13:24,039 --> 00:13:24,880
What brings you here?

359
00:13:24,880 --> 00:13:25,440
Your Majesty.

360
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:30,440
Father made me come here to accompany you.

361
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:32,359
He wouldn't be that nice.

362
00:13:32,559 --> 00:13:33,280
He was actually afraid that I'd run away.

363
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:34,440
That's why he asked you to keep an eye on me.

364
00:13:34,599 --> 00:13:36,359
Why would he? You're overthinking it.

365
00:13:36,359 --> 00:13:37,799
He didn't say anything.

366
00:13:39,359 --> 00:13:40,280
But what do you mean

367
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:42,400
in the broadcast?

368
00:13:42,799 --> 00:13:43,760
I mean...

369
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:46,520
It's a long story.

370
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:47,719
I have work to do.

371
00:13:47,719 --> 00:13:49,080
Just treat yourself at home.

372
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:49,799
I have to go.

373
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:51,080
I...

374
00:13:56,719 --> 00:13:57,359
Your Majesty.

375
00:13:57,719 --> 00:13:59,080
Go on and show us.

376
00:13:59,080 --> 00:13:59,960
Or you won't make it.

377
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:02,559
Why wouldn't I make it?

378
00:14:02,559 --> 00:14:03,679
I work fast.

379
00:14:03,679 --> 00:14:04,880
After I decided on the dishes,

380
00:14:04,880 --> 00:14:06,320
I'll get them done in an hour.

381
00:14:06,719 --> 00:14:07,760
Twenty dishes

382
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,359
in an hour?

383
00:14:09,359 --> 00:14:10,400
Twenty dishes?

384
00:14:10,880 --> 00:14:12,520
Duan Yunzhang is having 20 dishes?

385
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:14,159
Let me tell you, Your Majesty.

386
00:14:14,159 --> 00:14:16,039
His Majesty has 90 dishes every day.

387
00:14:16,159 --> 00:14:17,280
Thirty dishes for breakfast.

388
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:18,159
Forty dishes for lunch.

389
00:14:18,159 --> 00:14:19,200
Twenty dishes for dinner.

390
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:19,840
His Majesty

391
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,280
only asked you to make 20 dishes.

392
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:22,760
It's considered very kind of him to do so.

393
00:14:24,520 --> 00:14:25,400
Is he saying the truth?

394
00:14:26,599 --> 00:14:27,640
Yes, Your Majesty.

395
00:14:28,880 --> 00:14:29,799
(Fine.)

396
00:14:29,799 --> 00:14:31,520
(This is not about fulfilling a wife's duty.)

397
00:14:31,520 --> 00:14:34,000
(It's my husband trying to kill me.)

398
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:36,200
(Duan Yunzhang is trying to get rid of me)

399
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,479
(with this.)

400
00:14:37,479 --> 00:14:38,679
(That won't happen.)

401
00:14:40,119 --> 00:14:41,799
It's just 20 dishes.

402
00:14:41,799 --> 00:14:42,799
It's nothing.

403
00:14:45,280 --> 00:14:46,520
All of you, out.

404
00:14:46,679 --> 00:14:48,000
Don't get in my way.

405
00:14:48,280 --> 00:14:48,840
Go.

406
00:14:49,239 --> 00:14:50,640
Let's go.

407
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,159
Your Majesty.

408
00:14:53,159 --> 00:14:53,840
Sufang.

409
00:14:54,239 --> 00:14:55,760
We will begin our battle now.

410
00:14:57,640 --> 00:14:58,239
Add some noodles.

411
00:14:58,239 --> 00:14:58,880
Noodles.

412
00:14:58,880 --> 00:14:59,640
Two eggplants.

413
00:14:59,640 --> 00:15:00,479
♪Only second to the Emperor♪

414
00:15:00,479 --> 00:15:01,320
Some vegetables.

415
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:01,880
Yes.

416
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:05,119
♪Anyone who's against it should back off♪

417
00:15:06,280 --> 00:15:09,199
♪I'll make a face and fear no heaven and earth♪

418
00:15:09,520 --> 00:15:11,640
♪I'll let you go for now♪

419
00:15:11,640 --> 00:15:12,440
Right here.

420
00:15:13,040 --> 00:15:13,880
♪I'm not a motherly model♪

421
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:14,799
It's fresh.

422
00:15:15,560 --> 00:15:17,359
♪Nor am I the most beautiful lady♪

423
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:20,279
♪Who says those of humble origin
