424
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:22,559
♪Bring it on. Let's make a big bet♪

425
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:24,919
♪To be a huge winner♪

426
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:30,519
♪A couple of quarrelsome lovers♪

427
00:15:30,880 --> 00:15:33,839
♪By an odd coincidence to a much-told tale♪

428
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:37,599
♪Holding bad cards yet I play well still♪

429
00:15:37,599 --> 00:15:37,960
Here.

430
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:38,559
