431
00:15:38,559 --> 00:15:39,080
Sure.

432
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:40,279
♪Accept the plot twist♪

433
00:15:41,560 --> 00:15:44,119
♪Cut all the romantic themes♪

434
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:45,919
♪To talk about love is childish♪

435
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:48,519
♪I shall redefine peerless elegance♪

436
00:15:48,800 --> 00:15:50,919
