440
00:15:56,719 --> 00:15:57,640
A year?

441
00:15:58,280 --> 00:15:59,640
It's packed with flavors, so it's really good.

442
00:15:59,640 --> 00:16:01,039
Are you sure it's edible?

443
00:16:01,039 --> 00:16:01,760
Of course.

444
00:16:01,760 --> 00:16:02,640
It tastes wonderful.

445
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:03,599
You'll know when you taste it.

446
00:16:03,599 --> 00:16:05,239
♪Experiencing the ups and downs♪

447
00:16:05,239 --> 00:16:05,840
It's almost done.

448
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:06,760
♪In return for a wiser life♪

449
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:07,200
Just cover it up

450
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:08,400
and we can wait for it to cook.

451
00:16:08,880 --> 00:16:11,200
♪Don't ever look down♪

452
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:11,760
Let's go.

453
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:13,319
♪On the little crow♪

454
00:16:13,680 --> 00:16:17,039
♪She wears the crown and controls the world♪

455
00:16:17,280 --> 00:16:18,879
♪Striking back♪

456
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:22,919
♪To be the head of the harem♪

457
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:25,039
♪Little crow♪

458
00:16:25,420 --> 00:16:26,100
Let's see.

459
00:16:27,280 --> 00:16:28,919
♪Dear little crow♪

460
