00:16:36,980 --> 00:16:37,940
I'll lie down for a while.

465
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:41,479
♪A couple of quarrelsome lovers♪

466
00:16:41,800 --> 00:16:43,780
♪By an odd coincidence to a much-told tale♪

467
00:16:43,780 --> 00:16:44,500
It's done.

468
00:16:44,940 --> 00:16:45,700
Chai Tiezhou.

469
00:16:46,260 --> 00:16:47,180
It smells great.

470
00:16:47,180 --> 00:16:48,620
Chai Tiezhou, come in and have a look.

471
00:16:49,540 --> 00:16:50,620
No, you...

472
00:16:50,660 --> 00:16:50,980
Your Majesty.

473
00:16:50,980 --> 00:16:52,620
You made a pot stew?

474
00:16:52,620 --> 00:16:53,820
That's not how you should do it.

475
00:16:53,820 --> 00:16:55,220
That's what we do in Xianpa Village.

476
00:16:55,220 --> 00:16:56,180
What do you know?

477
00:16:56,460 --> 00:16:57,500
This is only one dish.

478
00:16:57,500 --> 00:16:58,580
What about the 20 dishes?

479
00:16:58,580 --> 00:16:59,500
♪I shall redefine peerless elegance♪

480
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:01,180
Give it a good look, all of you.

481
00:17:01,180 --> 00:17:01,820
Sufang.

482
00:17:02,260 --> 00:17:03,060
I need a plate.

483
00:17:03,060 --> 00:17:03,959
♪Tremble, my rivals♪

484
