♪On the little crow♪

494
00:17:24,180 --> 00:17:26,580
The third dish, braised eggplants.

495
00:17:26,580 --> 00:17:27,380
♪She wears the crown and controls the world♪

496
00:17:27,380 --> 00:17:28,100
What do you think?

497
00:17:28,319 --> 00:17:29,919
♪Striking back♪

498
00:17:30,040 --> 00:17:33,199
♪To be the head of the harem♪

499
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:36,260
♪Don't ever look down♪

500
00:17:36,260 --> 00:17:37,380
Just the right amount.

501
00:17:37,380 --> 00:17:39,180
Here are 20 dishes.

502
00:17:39,180 --> 00:17:41,180
♪She wears the crown and controls the world♪

503
00:17:41,180 --> 00:17:42,020
What are you looking at?

504
00:17:42,020 --> 00:17:43,100
Serve these dishes.

505
00:17:43,100 --> 00:17:44,940
Don't blame me if His Majesty gets hungry.

506
00:17:44,940 --> 00:17:46,300
♪To be the head of the harem♪

507
00:17:46,300 --> 00:17:46,900
Serve the dishes.

508
00:17:48,540 --> 00:17:49,060
Yes.

509
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:50,239
♪Little crow♪

510
00:17:53,580 --> 00:17:54,540
You are amazing, Your Majesty.

511
00:18:02,620 --> 00:18:03,220
Your Majesty.

512
00:18:03,420 --> 00:18:04,340
Lunch is...

513
00:18:04,340 --> 00:18:05,820
She failed, didn't she?

514
00:18:06,180 --> 00:18:07,740
She came out with all the dishes.

515
00:18:07,900 --> 00:18:08,500
What?

516
00:18:09,180 --> 00:18:10,620
She's done with the 20 dishes?

517
00:18:11,100 --> 00:18:11,820
Yes.

518
00:18:12,060 --> 00:18:13,060
Exactly 20 dishes.

519
00:18:15,060 --> 00:18:15,940
Throw them away.

520
00:18:16,540 --> 00:18:17,740
Get the Imperial Kitchen

521
00:18:17,740 --> 00:18:19,140
to prepare some food.

522
00:18:20,100 --> 00:18:20,700
Yes, Your Majesty.

523
00:18:21,660 --> 00:18:22,180
Wait.

524
00:18:24,300 --> 00:18:25,260
How are the dishes?

525
00:18:25,580 --> 00:18:27,340
They don't look the most appealing,

526
00:18:27,980 --> 00:18:29,540
but they smell quite good.

527
00:18:32,260 --> 00:18:33,940
The food on our plate

528
00:18:33,940 --> 00:18:35,100
doesn't come easily.

529
00:18:35,100 --> 00:18:36,380
It's shameful to be wasting food, isn't it?

530
00:18:36,860 --> 00:18:37,900
That's right.

531
00:18:53,100 --> 00:18:54,660
(It's not bad at all.)

532
00:18:58,900 --> 00:19:00,900
(It's as good as Chai's cooking.)

533
00:19:05,900 --> 00:19:06,540
Your Majesty.

534
00:19:07,300 --> 00:19:08,380
You have never

535
00:19:08,380 --> 00:19:10,340
enjoyed my food like how you are now.

536
00:19:11,900 --> 00:19:12,460
I haven't?

537
00:19:12,740 --> 00:19:13,380
You haven't.

538
00:19:13,660 --> 00:19:14,380
I treat people and things

539
00:19:15,380 --> 00:19:16,180
equally.

540
00:19:16,860 --> 00:19:17,700
You and the Queen

541
00:19:17,700 --> 00:19:18,980
are equally good at cooking.

542
00:19:21,220 --> 00:19:21,860
Your Majesty.

543
00:19:22,060 --> 00:19:22,820
Stop eating.

544
00:19:23,060 --> 00:19:24,020
How dare you?

545
00:19:26,060 --> 00:19:26,740
Your Majesty.

546
00:19:27,060 --> 00:19:27,700
Have you forgotten

547
00:19:27,700 --> 00:19:29,620
why you made her cook?

548
00:19:29,900 --> 00:19:31,380
Is it to prove

549
00:19:31,380 --> 00:19:31,980
that we are equally good?

550
00:19:31,980 --> 00:19:32,740
Right.

551
00:19:35,860 --> 00:19:36,700
I got careless.

552
00:19:37,780 --> 00:19:40,580
I wanted to put her in a difficult spot

553
00:19:40,580 --> 00:19:41,660
so that she couldn't take it

554
00:19:41,660 --> 00:19:42,460
and leave the palace.

555
00:19:42,900 --> 00:19:44,420
But I fell into her trap instead.

556
00:19:44,620 --> 00:19:45,740
Get up.

557
00:19:47,420 --> 00:19:48,220
I wanted to use this

558
00:19:48,220 --> 00:19:49,620
against her

559
00:19:49,820 --> 00:19:50,540
so that she quits

560
00:19:50,540 --> 00:19:51,380
and gets out of here.

561
00:19:51,380 --> 00:19:51,980
Yes.

562
00:19:52,380 --> 00:19:54,220
But she got me instead.

563
00:19:54,980 --> 00:19:55,820
Why don't we...

564
00:19:55,940 --> 00:19:57,100
I'll take these away immediately

565
00:19:57,100 --> 00:19:57,540
and serve other dishes.

566
00:19:57,540 --> 00:19:58,540
Let's get her to do laundry.

567
00:19:59,820 --> 00:20:01,340
Since cooking doesn't faze her,

568
00:20:01,460 --> 00:20:02,700
we'll exhaust her with the laundry work

569
00:20:02,780 --> 00:20:03,660
so that she has trouble sleeping.

570
00:20:10,660 --> 00:20:11,220
Your Majesty.

571
00:20:11,460 --> 00:20:12,180
What's wrong?

572
00:20:12,180 --> 00:20:12,660
Your Majesty.

573
00:20:12,660 --> 00:20:13,580
I don't feel good.

574
00:20:14,140 --> 00:20:15,220
The food is unhygienic.

575
00:20:16,860 --> 00:20:17,700
Go.

576
00:20:26,580 --> 00:20:27,220
Your Majesty.

577
00:20:27,340 --> 00:20:28,940
These are His Majesty's clothes.

578
00:20:28,940 --> 00:20:30,260
Please wash them clean

579
00:20:30,260 --> 00:20:31,420
by today.

580
00:20:32,020 --> 00:20:33,500
Why do I have to wash his clothes?

581
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:34,780
We have the Palace Laundry Service here, don't we?

582
00:20:34,980 --> 00:20:35,740
His Majesty has stated

583
00:20:36,380 --> 00:20:38,380
that it is a wife's duty

584
00:20:38,380 --> 00:20:39,900
to wash her husband's clothes.

585
00:20:39,900 --> 00:20:41,140
Duty again?

586
00:20:41,140 --> 00:20:42,500
He's trying to put me in a bind, isn't he?

587
00:20:43,620 --> 00:20:44,780
I will take my leave, Your Majesty.

588
00:20:47,420 --> 00:20:48,420
Fine.

589
00:20:48,980 --> 00:20:50,460
Who does he take me for?

590
00:20:50,820 --> 00:20:52,220
I won't give up that easily.

591
00:20:52,500 --> 00:20:53,140
Sufang.

592
00:20:53,300 --> 00:20:54,100
Go to the Palace Laundry Service

593
00:20:54,100 --> 00:20:55,340
and borrow some laundry items.

594
00:21:04,660 --> 00:21:05,260
Your Majesty.

595
00:21:05,260 --> 00:21:07,380
These are exquisite silk from Huzhou.

596
00:21:07,380 --> 00:21:07,980
I can't be bothered.

597
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:09,020
I'm running out of time.

598
00:21:09,020 --> 00:21:09,940
I'm sorry for this.

599
00:21:10,420 --> 00:21:10,980
Your Majesty.

600
00:21:11,220 --> 00:21:12,980
This is quite inappropriate.

601
00:21:13,260 --> 00:21:14,180
Forget it.

602
00:21:15,740 --> 00:21:16,300
This is...

603
00:21:18,980 --> 00:21:20,260
It's my duty to do the laundry, isn't it?

604
00:21:20,380 --> 00:21:22,500
What laundry work.

605
00:21:25,900 --> 00:21:26,540
Your Majesty.

606
00:21:27,100 --> 00:21:28,060
Who did this?

607
00:21:28,500 --> 00:21:29,460
Who else?

608
00:21:29,460 --> 00:21:30,540
It's the Queen.

609
00:21:30,740 --> 00:21:31,660
Not just this.

610
00:21:31,660 --> 00:21:32,220
Well...

611
00:21:34,820 --> 00:21:36,260
This is too much.

612
00:21:37,580 --> 00:21:38,220
Your Majesty,

613
00:21:38,220 --> 00:21:39,380
it's time to attend the assembly.

614
00:21:39,380 --> 00:21:40,140
I'm not going.

615
00:21:40,900 --> 00:21:41,620
No, that's...

616
00:21:41,620 --> 00:21:42,500
I know you're mad,

617
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:43,660
but you still have to attend the assembly.

618
00:21:43,660 --> 00:21:44,980
I'm not in the mood.

619
00:21:45,340 --> 00:21:45,980
Leave.

620
00:21:47,260 --> 00:21:48,020
Let's go.

621
00:21:54,780 --> 00:21:55,660
Liu Jinfeng.

622
00:21:56,860 --> 00:21:58,660
You have crossed the line.

623
00:21:59,380 --> 00:22:01,380
Don't blame me for being ruthless.

624
00:22:06,060 --> 00:22:07,620
What's with Duan Yunzhang again?

625
00:22:08,620 --> 00:22:09,500
Please see for yourself, Your Majesty.

626
00:22:09,500 --> 00:22:10,940
I can see it.

627
00:22:10,940 --> 00:22:12,260
It's dirty here, isn't it?

628
00:22:13,380 --> 00:22:14,660
Obviously.

629
00:22:14,660 --> 00:22:16,220
When was the last time this stable was cleaned?

630
00:22:16,220 --> 00:22:17,260
It stinks.

631
00:22:17,260 --> 00:22:17,900
I know.

632
00:22:17,900 --> 00:22:18,980
It hasn't been cleaned for three days.

633
00:22:18,980 --> 00:22:20,060
They were waiting for you.

634
00:22:20,380 --> 00:22:21,060
What?

635
00:22:25,100 --> 00:22:26,140
Greetings, Your Majesty.

636
00:22:26,140 --> 00:22:27,660
His Majesty has given his oral decree.

637
00:22:28,140 --> 00:22:29,060
He believes

638
00:22:29,180 --> 00:22:31,100
that the Queen is capable

639
00:22:31,100 --> 00:22:32,220
and diligent.

640
00:22:32,220 --> 00:22:35,020
She'll be able to clean the stable.

641
00:22:35,460 --> 00:22:36,340
Please do a good job.

642
00:22:36,660 --> 00:22:37,220
That's all to his statement.

643
00:22:38,460 --> 00:22:39,420
He sounded as if he was complimenting me.

644
00:22:39,420 --> 00:22:40,900
He's practically asking me to do labor work.

645
00:22:40,900 --> 00:22:41,980
Let me tell you.

646
00:22:41,980 --> 00:22:43,380
Horse manure is really useful.

647
00:22:43,540 --> 00:22:45,180
It is highly valued back in Xianpa Village.

648
00:22:45,180 --> 00:22:46,780
We use it to fertilize our plants.

649
00:22:47,420 --> 00:22:49,500
I won't bother you any longer, then.

650
00:22:49,780 --> 00:22:51,420
Take your time, Your Majesty.

651
00:22:52,220 --> 00:22:53,420
-Go.
-You brat!

652
00:22:53,620 --> 00:22:54,780
Go.

653
00:22:57,620 --> 00:22:58,260
Your Majesty.

654
00:22:58,940 --> 00:23:00,100
This place is filthy.

655
00:23:00,100 --> 00:23:01,940
Are you really going to clean it yourself?

656
00:23:01,940 --> 00:23:03,780
Nothing good comes out of Duan Yunzhang's mouth.

657
00:23:03,780 --> 00:23:04,940
But he's right about one thing.

658
00:23:04,940 --> 00:23:06,580
I am capable and diligent.

659
00:23:31,460 --> 00:23:33,460
It's been cleaned thoroughly.

660
00:23:34,820 --> 00:23:36,620
The bad smell is gone, too.

661
00:23:37,180 --> 00:23:38,980
Is this all done by the Queen?

662
00:23:39,860 --> 00:23:40,620
Your Majesty,

663
00:23:41,380 --> 00:23:42,820
not only did she clean it herself,

664
00:23:42,820 --> 00:23:44,300
but she also sent the horse manure

665
00:23:44,580 --> 00:23:48,220
to the plantation in the palace for compost.

666
00:23:49,620 --> 00:23:50,260
Not bad.

667
00:23:51,060 --> 00:23:52,900
I gave her such difficult tasks.

668
00:23:53,220 --> 00:23:54,940
Yet, she completed them

669
00:23:54,940 --> 00:23:56,780
without a word of complaint.

670
00:23:57,820 --> 00:23:59,460
Now she knows what I am capable of.

671
00:23:59,460 --> 00:24:00,060
It must be daunting for her.

672
00:24:00,940 --> 00:24:02,820
It's just that... She...

673
00:24:02,940 --> 00:24:03,900
What's wrong with her?

674
00:24:04,580 --> 00:24:05,660
She's fine.

675
00:24:06,100 --> 00:24:07,580
It's Yinyun.

676
00:24:09,340 --> 00:24:10,020
Yinyun?

677
00:24:17,780 --> 00:24:19,180
Where is my beloved horse?

678
00:24:20,220 --> 00:24:21,020
Where is it?

679
00:24:31,300 --> 00:24:32,620
What happened to you, Yinyun?

680
00:24:32,900 --> 00:24:33,780
What happened to its fur?

681
00:24:34,140 --> 00:24:35,780
When Her Majesty
was cleaning the stable yesterday,

682
00:24:36,740 --> 00:24:38,620
she noticed that Yinyun kept sneezing.

683
00:24:39,140 --> 00:24:41,100
She thought that it couldn't stand the heat,

684
00:24:41,380 --> 00:24:42,180
so...

685
00:24:42,580 --> 00:24:44,140
she shaved its fur.

686
00:24:45,780 --> 00:24:46,860
That woman.

687
00:24:47,420 --> 00:24:50,580
Never mind that she messed
with my stomach and clothes,

688
00:24:51,420 --> 00:24:53,580
but I can't believe she even messed with my horse.

689
00:24:54,420 --> 00:24:55,500
Yinyun, it's okay.

690
00:24:56,260 --> 00:24:57,660
I will revenge you.

691
00:24:59,260 --> 00:25:01,060
How long does it take for the fur to grow?

692
00:25:04,860 --> 00:25:05,700
It's all my fault

693
00:25:05,700 --> 00:25:07,500
for failing to protect you

694
00:25:07,820 --> 00:25:09,620
and putting you through such dishevelment.

695
00:25:10,140 --> 00:25:12,660
I feel so remorseful for the last few days.

696
00:25:12,980 --> 00:25:13,780
Why did I

697
00:25:13,780 --> 00:25:15,780
serve the poisoned dishes that day?

698
00:25:15,780 --> 00:25:17,620
You wouldn't have eaten it
if I hadn't served the food.

699
00:25:17,900 --> 00:25:18,540
If you hadn't eaten it,

700
00:25:18,540 --> 00:25:20,140
she wouldn't have to do the laundry.

701
00:25:20,140 --> 00:25:21,420
If she hadn't done the laundry,

702
00:25:21,620 --> 00:25:22,900
you wouldn't have let her clean the stable.

703
00:25:22,900 --> 00:25:23,340
If she hadn't cleaned the stable...

704
00:25:23,340 --> 00:25:23,860
Enough!

705
00:25:24,180 --> 00:25:25,300
You're being annoying.

706
00:25:25,420 --> 00:25:26,940
I don't care who her father is.

707
00:25:26,940 --> 00:25:28,100
The fact is that she has made His Majesty

708
00:25:28,100 --> 00:25:28,820
feel awful.

709
00:25:29,740 --> 00:25:30,380
This won't do.

710
00:25:30,380 --> 00:25:31,420
I will bring her here

711
00:25:31,420 --> 00:25:32,300
and let Your Majesty punish her.

712
00:25:35,780 --> 00:25:36,140
Jing.

713
00:25:36,140 --> 00:25:38,100
What's with the rush?

714
00:25:39,100 --> 00:25:39,980
To seize the Queen.

715
00:25:40,260 --> 00:25:41,020
Seize the Queen?

716
00:25:42,540 --> 00:25:43,380
Why?

717
00:25:51,020 --> 00:25:51,700
Yunzhang.

718
00:25:52,780 --> 00:25:55,180
What's with the long face?

719
00:25:56,500 --> 00:25:58,260
Is it because she...

720
00:26:01,340 --> 00:26:02,860
Don't bring her up.

721
00:26:03,020 --> 00:26:05,260
My body feels numb when I hear her name.

722
00:26:06,380 --> 00:26:07,420
That explains it.

723
00:26:08,860 --> 00:26:10,860
After my investigation
during the last couple of days,

724
00:26:11,140 --> 00:26:13,140
I found that the Queen is just like her father.

725
00:26:14,020 --> 00:26:15,060
They both are not simple.

726
00:26:15,420 --> 00:26:16,220
I'm all ears.

727
00:26:18,020 --> 00:26:18,620
Jing.

728
00:26:19,540 --> 00:26:20,220
Let me ask you.

729
00:26:20,740 --> 00:26:23,060
How many bowls of rice do you eat for a meal?

730
00:26:23,300 --> 00:26:23,900
Five bowls.

731
00:26:24,340 --> 00:26:25,420
You lose.

732
00:26:26,020 --> 00:26:27,860
You're a warrior,

733
00:26:28,260 --> 00:26:30,420
but you can't even win a woman?

734
00:26:30,700 --> 00:26:32,380
That's impossible.

735
00:26:33,420 --> 00:26:34,500
Ever since that day

736
00:26:34,780 --> 00:26:37,380
when my sister-in-law
humiliated Yunzhang as the despicable...

737
00:26:40,260 --> 00:26:42,740
I was utterly shocked anyhow.

738
00:26:43,060 --> 00:26:45,820
So, I got very curious about her.

739
00:26:46,620 --> 00:26:47,820
I went to Xiangluo Hall

740
00:26:47,820 --> 00:26:49,260
to talk to some of the servants there

741
00:26:51,660 --> 00:26:54,060
and got some good information.

742
00:26:57,700 --> 00:26:58,340
Yunzhang.

743
00:26:58,700 --> 00:26:59,780
Have a look.

744
00:27:03,220 --> 00:27:05,260
[The Queen eats at least five portions of rice every meal]
