(For the sake of His Majesty,)

995
00:35:58,940 --> 00:35:59,660
(I'll have to eat it.)

996
00:36:01,580 --> 00:36:02,900
(Can I not?)

997
00:36:04,820 --> 00:36:05,460
Help yourselves.

998
00:36:09,460 --> 00:36:10,180
Go on.

999
00:36:10,700 --> 00:36:12,420
All right.

1000
00:36:14,540 --> 00:36:15,500
Hurry up.

1001
00:36:21,420 --> 00:36:22,020
Your Majesty.

1002
00:36:22,820 --> 00:36:24,100
I've already had lunch.

1003
00:36:24,100 --> 00:36:24,620
How about this?

1004
00:36:24,620 --> 00:36:25,660
I'll drink with you.

1005
00:36:28,620 --> 00:36:29,660
Sure.

1006
00:36:34,340 --> 00:36:35,020
Sister-in-law.

1007
00:36:35,500 --> 00:36:36,700
Here's another toast.

1008
00:36:37,380 --> 00:36:38,620
Yunzhang is being unreasonable

1009
00:36:38,620 --> 00:36:39,460
this time.

1010
00:36:39,460 --> 00:36:40,380
You know better.

1011
00:36:40,380 --> 00:36:41,220
Your Majesty, here's another toast to you.

1012
00:36:41,220 --> 00:36:41,940
Sure.

1013
00:36:41,940 --> 00:36:42,420
Here.

1014
00:36:48,580 --> 00:36:49,860
I'll be honest.

1015
00:36:49,860 --> 00:36:52,220
This is some pretty good wine.

1016
00:36:52,220 --> 00:36:53,620
I'm getting drunk

1017
00:36:54,620 --> 00:36:55,540
after just a few cups.

1018
00:36:55,540 --> 00:36:56,180
[Jinfang Pavilion]

1019
00:36:56,180 --> 00:36:56,700
Your Majesty!

1020
00:36:56,900 --> 00:36:57,940
What happened?

1021
00:36:58,060 --> 00:36:58,620
Take her away.

1022
00:36:59,020 --> 00:36:59,660
Your Highness,

1023
00:36:59,740 --> 00:37:01,020
what's the meaning of this?

1024
00:37:01,260 --> 00:37:02,300
-Go away.
-This has nothing to do with you.

1025
00:37:02,500 --> 00:37:03,580
This is an order from His Majesty.

1026
00:37:04,060 --> 00:37:04,780
Your Majesty!

1027
00:37:04,980 --> 00:37:06,500
Where are you taking her?

1028
00:37:06,500 --> 00:37:08,060
I said it's an order from His Majesty.

1029
00:37:08,060 --> 00:37:08,580
You...

1030
00:37:10,260 --> 00:37:11,220
Just pretend that you see nothing.

1031
00:37:19,900 --> 00:37:20,540
Hurry up.

1032
00:37:25,231 --> 00:37:27,575
[Lingshu Academy]

1033
00:37:33,820 --> 00:37:35,260
The levee has fallen apart.

1034
00:37:35,260 --> 00:37:36,620
Flood is happening in many places.

1035
00:37:36,820 --> 00:37:38,420
People are losing their homes.

1036
00:37:38,700 --> 00:37:40,820
I hereby give my order
to distribute food relief to the flood victims

1037
00:37:41,460 --> 00:37:42,700
and carry out the repair work.

1038
00:37:43,340 --> 00:37:44,380
These two tasks
are to be carried out at the same time.

1039
00:37:45,580 --> 00:37:46,700
Neither one of them can be compromised.

1040
00:37:50,180 --> 00:37:51,180
Accept my order.

1041
00:37:53,420 --> 00:37:54,100
Your Majesty.

1042
00:37:54,420 --> 00:37:56,580
I suggest discussing this

1043
00:37:56,580 --> 00:37:57,580
with the Grand Chancellor.

1044
00:38:01,700 --> 00:38:02,500
You're asking me to wait?

1045
00:38:04,060 --> 00:38:05,340
This is urgent!

1046
00:38:05,940 --> 00:38:07,020
I'm fine with waiting.

1047
00:38:07,700 --> 00:38:09,300
But what about the victims?

1048
00:38:12,340 --> 00:38:13,020
Your Majesty.

1049
00:38:13,020 --> 00:38:14,380
Sufang would like to meet you.

1050
00:38:17,060 --> 00:38:17,900
Let her in.

1051
00:38:18,140 --> 00:38:18,700
Yes.

1052
00:38:19,660 --> 00:38:20,380
Come in.

1053
00:38:25,260 --> 00:38:25,860
Your Majesty.

1054
00:38:26,100 --> 00:38:28,740
I saw Prince Yunchong and Commander Su

1055
00:38:28,740 --> 00:38:31,340
taking Her Majesty to the Lingshu Academy
after knocking her out with wine.

1056
00:38:31,580 --> 00:38:34,940
Is that an order from you?

1057
00:38:35,860 --> 00:38:37,420
(They are already on the move.)

1058
00:38:38,100 --> 00:38:39,300
(That's quick.)

1059
00:38:40,740 --> 00:38:41,740
That's right.

1060
00:38:41,900 --> 00:38:42,660
It's nothing.

1061
00:38:43,020 --> 00:38:43,980
But...

1062
00:38:45,940 --> 00:38:46,860
Yes.

1063
00:38:47,580 --> 00:38:48,700
I'll excuse myself.

1064
00:38:55,180 --> 00:38:55,820
Your Majesty.

1065
00:38:56,220 --> 00:38:57,740
In our opinion,

1066
00:38:57,900 --> 00:39:00,020
why don't we select a few urgent matters

1067
00:39:00,060 --> 00:39:02,100
and bring them over

1068
00:39:02,100 --> 00:39:03,420
to the Grand Chancellor's Residence

1069
00:39:03,980 --> 00:39:06,140
so that he can have a look first?

1070
00:39:08,900 --> 00:39:09,980
That's right.

1071
00:39:10,420 --> 00:39:10,980
Your Majesty.

1072
00:39:13,300 --> 00:39:13,860
All right.

1073
00:39:14,940 --> 00:39:18,180
Go climb over the wall and discuss this
with the Grand Chancellor.

1074
00:39:18,540 --> 00:39:20,820
Do inform me when a decision has been made.

1075
00:39:21,700 --> 00:39:22,180
I...

1076
00:39:22,540 --> 00:39:23,100
We wouldn't dare to do so.

1077
00:39:23,100 --> 00:39:24,420
Right now!

1078
00:39:28,060 --> 00:39:29,140
To the Lingshu Academy now.

1079
00:39:29,340 --> 00:39:29,900
Yes.

1080
00:39:44,700 --> 00:39:45,260
Sufang.

1081
